quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,49,"Tí kò bá jẹ́ pé ìkẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀ lé e bá, wọn ìbá jù ú sórí ilẹ̀ gban̄sasa (láti inú ẹja) ní ẹni-èébú."
  68,50,"Nítorí náà, Olúwa rẹ̀ ṣà á lẹ́ṣà. Ó sì ṣe é ní ara àwọn ẹni rere."
  68,51,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ fẹ́ẹ̀ fi ojú wọn gbé ọ ṣubú nígbà tí wọ́n gbọ́ ìrántí náà. Wọ́n sì ń wí pé: “Dájúdájú wèrè mà ni.”"
  69,46,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Àwa ìbá já isan ọrùn rẹ̀."
  69,47,"Kò sì sí ẹnì kan nínú yín tí ó máa gbà á sílẹ̀ lọ́wọ́ (Wa)."
  69,48,"Dájúdájú (al-Ƙur’ān) ni ìrántí fún àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu)."
  70,40,"Nítorí náà, Èmi ń fi Olúwa àwọn ibùyọ òòrùn àti àwọn ibùwọ̀ òòrùnbúra, dájúdájú Àwa ni Alágbára {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, Èmi, Olúwa àwọn ibùyọ òòrùn àti ibùwọ̀ òòrùn ń fi ara Mi búra. Wòóore: Èròǹgbà Allāhu pẹ̀lú “mọṣriƙ” àti “mọgrib” nínú sūrah al-Muzzammil; 73:9 ni agbègbè ibùyọ òòrùn àti agbègbè ibùwọ̀ òòrùn. Èròǹgbà Allāhu pẹ̀lú “mọṣriƙọen” nínú sūrah ar-Rahmọ̄n; 55:17 ni ibùyọ òòrùn lásìkò ẹ̀rùn àti ibùyọ òòrùn lásìkò òjò. Bákan náà, “mọgribaen” ibùwọ̀ òòrùn lásìkò ẹ̀rùn àti ibùwọ̀ òòrùn lásìkò òjò. Bákan náà, èròǹgbà Allāhu pẹ̀lú “mọṣāriƙ àti mọgārib” ni àwọn ọgọ́sàn-án ibùyọ òòrùn àti ọgọ́sàn-án ibùwọ̀ òòrùn. (Tafsīr Bagawiy)]
  70,41,"láti lè fi àwọn tó dára jù wọ́n lọ pààrọ̀ wọn. Kò sì sí ẹni tó lè kó agara bá Wa.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ tún wo sūrah al-Wāƙi‘ah; 56:60-61 àti sūrah al-Ƙiyāmọh; 75:3-4.]
  70,42,"Nítorí náà, fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ kí wọ́n máa sọ ìsọkúsọ (wọn), kí wọ́n sì máa ṣeré títí wọn yóò fi pàdé ọjọ́ wọn tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún wọn."
  74,25,"Kí ni èyí bí kò ṣe ọ̀rọ̀ abara”"
  74,26,"Èmi yóò fi sínú iná Saƙọr."
  74,27,"Kí l’ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ iná Saƙọr?"
  75,22,"Àwọn ojú kan ní ọjọ́ yẹn yóò tutù (fún ìdùnnú)."
  75,23,"Olúwa wọn ni wọn yóò máa wò."
  75,24,"Àwọn ojú kan ní ọjọ́ yẹn sì máa bàjẹ́."
  76,16,"Ife aláwo tí wọ́n ṣe láti ara fàdákà ni (wọ́n). A sì ṣe wọ́n níwọ̀n- níwọ̀n (tí ó ṣe wẹ́kú ohun tí wọ́n fẹ́ mu)."
  76,17,"Àti pé wọn yóò máa fún wọn ní ife ọtí kan mu nínú (Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra). Ohun tí A pòpọ̀ mọ́ (ọtí náà) ni atalẹ̀."
  76,18,"Nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra (wọn yóò tún máa mu) omi ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú kan, tí À ń pè ní omi salsabīl."
  77,13,"Fún ọjọ́ ìpínyà (láààrin àwọn ẹ̀dá) ni."
  77,14,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Ọjọ́ ìpínyà?"
  77,15,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  78,10,"A tún ṣe alẹ́ ní ìbora."
  78,11,"A tún ṣe ọ̀sán ní (àsìkò fún) wíwá ìjẹ-ìmu."
  78,12,"A tún mọ sánmọ̀ méje tó lágbára sókè yín."
  79,4,"Ó tún fi àwọn mọlāika tó máa ṣíwájú ẹ̀mí àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo wọnú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra tààrà búra."
  79,5,"Ó tún fi àwọn mọlāika tó ń ṣètò nínú sánmọ̀ àti ilé ayé pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Allāhu búra."
  79,6,"Ní ọjọ́ tí ìmìtìtì máa mi gbogbo ayé tìtì.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ní ọjọ́ tí ìfọn àkọ́kọ́ fún òpin ayé máa ṣẹlẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ohùn igbe tó máa le pin.]
  80,1,"Ó fajú ro, ó sì pẹ̀yìndà1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - fajú ro, ó sì pẹ̀yìndà.]
  80,2,"nítorí pé afọ́jú wá bá a."
  80,3,"Kí sì l’ó máa fi mọ̀ ọ́ pé ó ṣeé ṣe kí ó ṣàfọ̀mọ́ (ara rẹ̀ kúrò nínú àìgbàgbọ́)"